Ranger Help for: move silently
================================

SYNTAX:      smove <direction>
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,road,beach,
             underground,mountain,arctic,barren
SLOT COST:   7
BASE SP:     20
SKILL TYPE:  stealth

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to move to an adjacent room without being
noticed by other creatures or players. The chance of being detected
depends on the Ranger's dexterity, skill level, and the terrain. Some
terrains are easier to move silently through than others. Forests and
swamps offer natural cover, while open plains and roads are more
difficult. Moving silently is essential for setting up ambushes or
avoiding dangerous encounters.
